<main class="artic-word-main">
    <h2 class="artic-word-heading">ITSM Form Instructions</h2>
    <p>Please read the following instructions carefully before filling out any ITSM form:</p>
    <hr />
    <h3>Required Fields</h3>
    <p>Any field marked with an asterisk <strong>(<span style="color:red;">*</span></strong> is mandatory and must be completed before submission.</p>
    <hr />
    <h3>Key Information</h3>
    <p>Some important information (such as name or title) cannot be duplicated with existing data in the system. Please ensure that you use a unique value when filling out the form.</p>
    <hr />
    <h3>Incident Form</h3>
    <p>The Incident form is divided into three sections:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Form Section:</strong> For entering detailed information about the incident.</li>
        <li><strong>Communication Section:</strong> For discussing the progress of the incident.</li>
        <li><strong>Resolution Section:</strong> For recording the resolution method of the incident.</li>
    </ul>
    <hr />
    <h3>Other Forms</h3>
    <p>Other forms generally only contain the form section and do not include separate communication or resolution sections.</p>
    <hr />
    <h3>Having Trouble?</h3>
    <p>If you are unable to submit the form or encounter any issues, please contact the IT department for assistance.</p>

</main>
